Transcription.Text: He 'd thrown his pride to the wind and accepted Charlie's superiority in seduction. And it was hard to imagine a prettier teacher. To have her twist in an attempt to receive a caress he was purposely withholding, to hear her deep-throated moan of full satisfaction and feel her shivering, clawing surrender.
